cars being reclaimed in less than 14 days

48:24.200 --> 48:27.600
must be left in lots L, M or N.

48:38.800 --> 48:41.000
The King of New York.

48:44.200 --> 48:46.300
- Congratulations.
- Thanks, Tony.

48:46.335 --> 48:48.500
You deserve it.

48:49.800 --> 48:54.700
I want you to know this is the last time
we'll meet like this. It's undignified.

49:00.400 --> 49:04.100
So, what's the word on your cousin?

49:10.900 --> 49:13.300
I think I know where he's holed up.

49:16.600 --> 49:17.665
And?

49:17.700 --> 49:20.300
I know this has to be done, John,

49:20.400 --> 49:23.800
but I'm asking you now as a friend.

49:25.200 --> 49:28.800
- Let me handle this myself.
- I can't do that, Tony.

49:31.300 --> 49:34.700
You can do whatever the fuck you want,
you're the fuckin' boss.

49:34.800 --> 49:36.900
I choose not to, then.

49:45.200 --> 49:47.165
I want your promise it'll be quick.

49:47.200 --> 49:49.900
I'm not gonna lie to you, Tony, I don't have to.

49:50.000 --> 49:53.200
Phil's gonna do it, and he'll do it his way.

49:57.500 --> 50:01.400
This is me now. Come on.

50:02.800 --> 50:04.900
Anything else?

50:08.300 --> 50:09.900
No.

50:31.000 --> 50:34.400
You know what, John? I'll give you undignified.

50:35.200 --> 50:36.800
Go fuck yourself.

50:38.000 --> 50:39.800
You and Phil and whoever.

50:42.000 --> 50:43.700
He's my fuckin' cousin.

51:21.400 --> 51:25.400
- You all right?
- This is some funny shit.

51:30.300 --> 51:32.300
What the fuck is wrong with you?

51:38.500 --> 51:40.400
I snorted a little H.

51:43.600 --> 51:45.900
I know, but...

51:47.100 --> 51:50.700
I can't stand the pain. I loved her.

51:56.800 --> 51:58.600
Fuckin' pain, huh?

52:01.400 --> 52:03.700
You think you're alone in this?

52:03.800 --> 52:06.500
It was a judgment call. She sounded OK.

52:06.600 --> 52:08.265
The status on Moltisanti?

52:08.300 --> 52:10.565
Seen yesterday leaving the Bing with Tony.

52:10.600 --> 52:13.265
- Should we bring him in?
- That'll get us nothing.

52:13.300 --> 52:17.100
She really could have fled.
She could be in China by now.

52:31.000 --> 52:33.000
How should we handle the Nieves murder?

52:33.035 --> 52:34.965
We have the terror possibility.

52:35.000 --> 52:37.600
Take it over from the Long Branch PD.

53:23.400 --> 53:25.700
Well, what did I say, is it beautiful?

53:29.700 --> 53:31.700
Yeah, it's a gorgeous piece of land.

53:32.700 --> 53:36.600
With this view, it's well worth 600,000.

53:37.600 --> 53:40.100
The surveyor's coming on Tuesday.

53:58.000 --> 54:01.000
- You all right?
- Yeah. Me? Yeah.

54:01.600 --> 54:03.600
Absolutely.

